{
  "stem": "1641.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We have here people ranging from 50,000 to 100,000, and each time more transports come in, then they gas as many as-- as the crematorium can burn.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And their-- additional, the surplus stocks, go to Birkenau, where they're kept in reserve.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then there is the day when there's a no-- no train coming, which happened after the Hungarian Jews were all fixed up, liquidated.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then when there were-- a week when there were no trains coming, then on that week, they pull out every day 10,000, 20,000 people from Birkenau, and then they gas them, using up their reserves.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So to say, they-- they reserve raw material-- like reserve for the fire, for the-- for the-- for the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was their reserve.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only exception was, which they didn't use up at that stage, was the gypsy camp, which was only used up around June or July.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then there was the Theresienstadt camp where who could keep their civilian clothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were eventually burnt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- they were gassed, but not yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were gassed later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I believe they were gassed around November.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was October or November.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were not gassed in June, July.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were kept.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't know what to do with them, quite, but eventually they decided that they should be gassed too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in the meantime, this fellow was very sad, because he said, you're going to Auschwitz, but I'm here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And could be a quiet day next week or in the fortnight, when I will be gassed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw many, many groups of people driven a savage way to the-- towards the gas chamber next day, in a different-- not our block, but next door where the others were.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
